template<class T>
VectorProxy< T >::VectorProxy (  vector< T > &  realVector,
int  startIdx,
int  size
)  [inline]
 

Creates a new VectorProxy using the real vector from position startIdx to position startIdx + size.

<br/> BE CAREFUL! There must be enough room for the maximum size that this vector will have in the other vector.

Parameters:
realVector Real vector where the storage is.
startIdx Start index in the real vector. Will never change.
